25 SUMMARY
2266 This bill amends the law governing dedimus justices by requiring the appointment of
2277 2 county employees and one sheriff's department employee in each county to perform the
2288 duties of dedimus justice on behalf of county government and the county sheriff,
2299 respectively. The bill also requires the Secretary of State to maintain a roster of persons
3300 designated as dedimus justices and make the roster available on the Secretary of State's
3311 publicly accessible website.
